# Keep the Docker build context clean and reproducible.
#
# The runtime host image is built with `COPY . .` then `dotnet publish`. Local
# build outputs must NOT leak into the context: a host-built obj/ (e.g. a macOS
# wasmtime-dotnet native bundle) makes the in-container build skip the fresh
# Linux native-library download/extract and fail with MSB3030.

# .NET build outputs
**/bin/
**/obj/
artifacts/

# Test / tooling output
**/TestResults/

# IDE / editor state
**/.vs/
**/.vscode/
**/.idea/

# OS cruft
**/.DS_Store
